{"tid":1253727,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警犬濫用救護車，推到醫護同消防助攻","createTime":"2019-06-23T17:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T17:41:40.000Z","uid":182802,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a98b4fb9b5f931a7596e6753c718d66a787682f4","tid":1253727,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:17:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/654870348270867/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F654870348270867%2F&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr17sYlYTGbxuQQGsxDmAgPG8%3D&h=b5e42918\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/654870348270867/</a><br />\n&quot;<strong>警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉</strong>指，據其了解，當日有13人需要救護員治理，包括懷孕婦女、長期病患者等，他們圍困多個小時後身體不適，召救護車是理所當然。<br />\n他又指，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>若有人在救護車得到適當治療後，無需要再使用急症室服務，是常有的事</strong></span>。他認為此舉可以更有效運用醫療資源。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>1) 醫護</ins></strong><br />\n- 救護員主要負責送院前護理，其中包括<span style=\"color: blue;\">檢查/ 維持維生指數 (Vital signs)</span>，或就病徵提供初步治療；而搵出不適嘅原因同<span style=\"color: blue;\">診斷 (Diagnosis</span>) 係醫生嘅工作<br />\n- 好多病嘅病徵非常反覆，好多時<span style=\"color: blue;\">病徵消失唔代表問題解決</span>，仍然需要睇醫生做詳細檢查。經典例子： <ins><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">小中風 (TIA)</span></strong></ins>：<br />\n(I)＂小中風發作相當迅速，由未有徵狀到症狀明顯，只需五分鐘。<span style=\"color: blue;\">發病後二十四小時內，徵狀會完全消失</span>。小中風是<span style=\"color: blue;\">中風警號</span>，表示病情已經達至危險程度，<span style=\"color: blue;\">需要即時治療</span>。請即致電９９９送院求<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.strokefund.org/stroke_part1.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.strokefund.org%2Fstroke_part1.php&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr17sYlYTGbxuQQGsxDmAgPG8%3D&h=8ef7c058\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.strokefund.org/stroke_part1.php</a><br />\n<br />\n(II) &quot;中文大學研究發現，若病人能在出現<span style=\"color: blue;\">小中風病徵24小時內求診、並獲得治療</span>，可<span style=\"color: blue;\">降低</span>3個月內<span style=\"color: blue;\">再次中風的風險高達7成</span>。&quot; <a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1412427/%E5%9B%9B%E8%82%A2%E4%B9%8F%E5%8A%9B%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%8F%E4%B8%AD%E9%A2%A8%E3%80%8D%E5%85%88%E5%85%86%20%20%20%E6%8A%8A%E6%8F%A124%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82%E6%9C%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1412427%2F%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%2582%25A2%25E4%25B9%258F%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%2598%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%2585%2586%2520%2520%2520%25E6%258A%258A%25E6%258F%25A124%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%25BB%2583%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%2599%2582%25E6%259C%259F&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr17sYlYTGbxuQQGsxDmAgPG8%3D&h=604c9efa\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1412427/%E5%9B%9B%E8%82%A2%E4%B9%8F%E5%8A%9B%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%8F%E4%B8%AD%E9%A2%A8%E3%80%8D%E5%85%88%E5%85%86%20%20%20%E6%8A%8A%E6%8F%A124%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82%E6%9C%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n警犬公開表示＂如果市民喺救護車上得到適當治療，沒有生命危險，通常唔需要去急症室＂呢個講法有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>誤導</strong></span>成份，<span style=\"color: red;\">推翻醫護近年積極喺基層醫療 (Primary care)推廣健康資訊，提高市民求醫意識嘅工作</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2) 消防</ins></strong><br />\n- 雖然消防署未有就濫用救護車作定義，但網頁上有提到＂消防處救護車為境內包括離島居民提供緊急救護服務，市民遇有急病或受傷而<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">未能自行求診者</span></strong>可致電 999 熱線或直撥消防處救護車調派中心電話2735 3355 要求緊急救護服務。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在可能情況下，如非嚴重傷病</span></strong>，例如日炙以致皮膚紅癢等，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">市民應利用其他途徑往醫院求診</span></strong>。＂<a href=\"https://www.hkfsd.gov.hk/chi/source/safety/Ambulance_Services_in_HK.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfsd.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fsource%2Fsafety%2FAmbulance_Services_in_HK.pdf&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr17sYlYTGbxuQQGsxDmAgPG8%3D&h=30270c16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfsd.gov.hk/chi/source/safety/Ambulance_Services_in_HK.pdf</a><br />\n- 警犬而家等於<span style=\"color: red;\">公開鼓勵市民喺非緊急情況下使用救護車</span><br />\n<br />\n有冇可能一人一信推到醫護同消防出黎助攻?"},{"pid":"17d5bbe36eadecbb6d5bf968bfe9cb3864665630","tid":1253727,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:42:37.000Z","msg":"push 求意見"},{"pid":"7244324f4c2f12dc1b450ae36a3a30b19fb16293","tid":1253727,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:40:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab25645366ad72ec0cc4cc33c32bd83e00000dc3","tid":1253727,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:41:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}